### Development Environment
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@apiVersion = v1
@apiPrefix = /api/{{apiVersion}}

### Full API URL
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}

### Common Headers
@contentType = application/json

### Test Delay (untuk rate limiting test)
@testDelay = 1000

